{"word":"ἀνερωτάω","slug":"ἀνερωτάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνερωτάω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to ask</i> or <i>inquire of, question</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to ask about, inquire into</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; so, <el>ἀν. περί τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> dupl. <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to question</i> a person about a thing, <i>ask</i> it of him, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}